name: U-Part Wigs
description:
These units are made to cut down the time of the traditional sew in weave, They are made to be sewn around the perimeter of your head and can be worn with a middle part or a side part. With these you can manage your natural hair better and more frequently. U-Part orders must  be ordered over the phone, in person or via email because of every bodys wants and needs are different and the prices may vary.
